"<1.so>My name is Nazbi, treasure hunter and\n"
"adventurer extraordinaire!\n"
"\n"
"I long for adventure as a weary traveler\n"
"longs for a warm bed. Right now, I'm in\n"
"pursuit of the legend of the dragon!\n"
"It's a pursuit that has kept me quite\n"
