msgctxt "SavedLv1_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>A bold adventurer such as myself would\n"
"have been fine on his own, but from one\n"
"traveler to another...<2.pa> Thank you."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "SavedLv1_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I just wasn't in a fighting mood is all.<2.pa>\n"
"Thanks for taking that off my plate."
msgstr ""

