#. 2: sound
#. 3: pause (short)
msgctxt "SavedLv3_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>All's well that ends well, as long as\n"
"everyone is alive and well!\n"
"\n"
"<2.so>Huh? That makes it sound like all I did\n"
"was sit back and watch?<3.pa> What an astute\n"
"observation!"
msgstr ""

